law.history: Repealed 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 406, sec. 336, effective January 1, 1975. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 5, sec. 1. -- Amended 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 145, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 1960, 1961.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Operating gambling machine, game or contrivance -- Pools at race tracks and pinball machines exempted.
